Saliba on why he picked Arsenal over Spurs:<br />
<br />
&quot;The history, the badge... since I was little, I've been watching Arsenal play. There are a lot of French players who have come through here. So that really helped me to make my mind up. This is the biggest club in England for me.&quot;

